Download data dictionary for geospatial data

Source: R/documentation.R
dictionary.Rd

Download data dictionary for geospatial data

Usage

dictionary(dataset)

Arguments

dataset

character with the dataset name

Value

tibble with data dictionary

Examples

dictionary("DANE_MGNCNPV_2018_SETU")
